OL,3,CRelief for Channel Island athletes as
OL,4,C2026 Commonwealths confirmed for
OL,5,CGlasgow
OL,7,FAthletes and coaches in Guernsey and
OL,8,FJersey have been expressing their
OL,9,Fexcitement and relief that the 2026
OL,10,FCommonwealth Games will take place
OL,11,Fafter months of uncertainty.
OL,13,FGlasgow was announced today (18
OL,14,FSeptember) as host city after the
OL,15,FAustralian state of Victoria pulled
OL,16,Fout of holding the Games in July 2023
OL,17,Fover concerns about cost.
