OL,5,CGlasgow
OL,7,FGuernsey's 400m hurdler Alastair
OL,8,FChalmers, who made the semi-finals in
OL,9,Fhis Olympic debut in Paris this
OL,10,Fsummer, says representing the island
OL,11,Fmeans a lot.
OL,13,FHe said: "For me it is really running
OL,14,Ffor Guernsey. Whenever I'm at the
OL,15,FOlympics or the Worlds or Europeans,
OL,16,Fit's always for GB which is such an
OL,17,Fhonour as well but coming from such a
OL,18,Fsmall island and a tight community, I
OL,19,Fwant to represent that.
