OL,7,F"So definitely, for myself, it's
OL,8,Fputting us on the map a little bit."
OL,10,FSara Parfit, who coaches the Guernsey
OL,11,Fswimming team told ITV News: "The
OL,12,Fswimmers are very excited to hear
OL,13,Fwe've actually got a venue. That's the
OL,14,Fkey thing first of all but I think for
OL,15,Fmany of the swimmers that went to
OL,16,FBirmingham, the reception they
OL,17,Freceived in Birmingham, being a home
OL,18,Fnation, was just out of this world so
OL,19,FI'm excited that we are going to get
OL,20,Fthe same sort of reaction from the
OL,21,Fcrowds in Scotland as well."
