OL,7,FOver in Jersey, the decision to give
OL,8,FGlasgow the Games has been welcomed
OL,9,Ftoo.
OL,11,FPaul Huddlestone, president of the
OL,12,FCommonwealth Games Association of
OL,13,FJersey described the Games as "the
OL,14,Fpinnacle" of sporting achievement for
OL,15,Fislanders.
