OL,5,CGlasgow
OL,7,FMr Huddlestone said: "It really is a
OL,8,Ffantastic experience, both on the
OL,9,Ffield of plauy and in the village
OL,10,Fwhere they can meet other athletes and
OL,11,Fother coaches form around the world
OL,12,Fwhich is a just a fantastic
OL,13,Fexperience."
OL,15,FHe added that Jersey has several
OL,16,Fprospects for the 2026 Commonwealths
OL,17,Fin sports which are yet to be
OL,18,Fconfirmed, including triathlon and
OL,19,Fgymnastics.
